And if I asked him to come into my heart, he would take control of my life, which again made no sense.

00:40:48.547 --> 00:40:54.898
Nevertheless, I felt totally lost and did say to Jesus, come into my heart and take control of my life.

00:40:55.940 --> 00:41:07.058
Many think I'm nuts when I tell them that I heard the audible voice of God who said he would come into my life and take control, just a sentence, but the peace

00:41:07.682 --> 00:41:16.571
that passes all understanding doesn't begin to describe what happened to my body, soul and spirit right then.

00:41:17.752 --> 00:41:22.076
I began shouting, Chris, God is gonna control my life.

00:41:23.177 --> 00:41:27.081
He began to pray while others around were saying out loud that I was tripping.

00:41:28.422 --> 00:41:32.446
I went home, got a Bible and read the four Gospels out loud.

00:41:33.307 --> 00:41:36.370
Three months later, I had a teaching position

00:41:36.610 --> 00:41:46.088
at second grade at a Christian school, lots of interesting journeys up and down, but God has never failed.

00:41:47.811 --> 00:41:51.939
Don't we want everybody to have an experience like Sue?

00:41:53.281 --> 00:41:57.810
If God has changed our hearts, then we can't help but tell people.
